      "rationale": "PIV validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — the same geometry used in the COU. Operating conditions span the full COU envelope. Blood analog fluid properties match clinical blood rheology within accepted approximation. Validation activities are directly applicable to COU."
